  "body": "The chainId and networkId for a local test network should match. Since dev mode is a quick and easy way to setup the dev network, it shouldn't need creating a custom genesis config.\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.9.11-stable\r\nOS & Version: OSX\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nSpecifying `--networkId` should set the genesis `chainId`\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nThe same chainId `1337` is used regardless of the networkId. A custom genesis config needs to be constructed.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\n1. geth --dev --networkId 33\r\n2. See `ChainId` in the console `Initialised chain configuration` will be set to 1337\r\n",
