    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Chain ID and network ID are different concepts. Whilst it might make sense to maybe have the network id default to the chain ID, but definitely not the other way around. We don't want the consensus rules to change due to some network flag.\r\n\r\nDev more also is just a quick way to run (unit) tests locally. If you are entering networking territory, just spin up a proper private network. Dev mode isn't meant for that and we should not make it smarter than it's supposed to be.",
